    "scope": "D3",
    "claim_type": "definition",
    "status": "active",
    "claim": "A mantrap (airlock) is a two-door entry with only one door open at a time; it prevents tailgating. The person must be authenticated before the inner door opens, ensuring only one authorized individual enters per cycle.",
